title: SO Launcher Prime (Galaxy S7 launcher) v1.92 APK (Android)
description:
SO Launcher, is the most polished, highly customizable galaxy s6 style launcher. Smooth, Rich features, NO AD

Features:
Support icon theme, compatible with 5000+ icon packs and themes
Galaxy s6 TouchWiz Launcher scrolling effect
Support drawer app sorting, drawer folder, app hiding
Handy Sidebar: include Cleaner, Toggle, Torch etc; and you can drag-out Sidebar from anywhere
Many gestures and Dock icon gestures
Unread Counts/Notifier for SMS, MAIL, Missed CALL and Whatsapp etc
Translucent status bar and navigation bar for Android4.4, Android 5.0 devices, and Galaxy S6, Galaxy Note devices.
Backup and restore launcher setting and layout; Import layout from other launcher
Highly customizable, include 200+ options:
Change launcher desktop and drawer grid size, edit icon, lock desktop, etc
4 UI Size Mode, easy to change the icon size
4 Drawer style: Horizontal, Vertical, Vertical with category, List style
Many Desktop and Drawer transition effect; Many Live wallpapers
